8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 22=

11
00:00:43,560 --> 00:00:44,359
(Keep going.)

12
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,799
(Live well, even just for me.)

13
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:49,119
Jian.

14
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:17,680
My mother's life,

15
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,920
your parents' lives,

16
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:22,680
Pei Du's ambition,

17
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:25,200
and Su Jian's sacrifice.

18
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:30,599
I'll make Murong Che pay for it all

19
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,879
with his blood.

20
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,079
Once we've had our revenge,

21
00:01:41,359 --> 00:01:42,760
let's leave all this behind

22
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,519
and live our lives.

23
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,000
Your Majesty,

24
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:59,599
Prince Xuanlie captured Yue Qin alive.

25
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:01,480
The officials have all petitioned,

26
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,840
urging you to name him the Crown Prince.

27
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:07,200
Did you find Prince Jinghe?

28
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:08,800
Your Majesty,

29
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,919
Prince Jinghe is still missing.

30
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,560
The search parties found nothing.

31
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:16,080
Then force him out.

32
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,159
I want him found,

33
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,680
alive or dead.

34
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:22,240
Let's see

35
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:24,240
how long he can hide!

36
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,639
Yiyi,

37
00:02:38,719 --> 00:02:40,039
Jinghe's grown up.

38
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:43,120
I want our son
to become the Crown Prince.

39
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,759
But he won't listen to me.

40
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,479
Just like you, he never listens to me!

41
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,400
Why?

42
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:52,560
Why?

43
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,759
Your Highness,
your firewood-cutting skills

44
00:03:01,759 --> 00:03:03,319
are not as sharp as your swordplay.

45
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,199
Then teach me.

46
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,000
We've got plenty of time here.

47
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,000
Take it slow.

48
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:22,719
The Emperor's already issued a decree.

49
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,479
We're fugitives now.

50
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,960
This won't last much longer.

51
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,840
So what do you think?

52
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:31,080
No one can hide forever.

53
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:33,000
And nothing waits forever either.

54
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,439
You know,

55
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,639
not acting is the act itself.

56
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:42,960
Our absence

57
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,840
doesn't make us invisible.

58
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:48,680
So, do you accept such fate or deny it?

59
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,319
I just realized it.

60
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,240
Hiding here these days
is more like a life stolen.

61
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,000
And it must be repaid.

62
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:58,080
And then?

63
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,520
Then I steal it back.

64
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,479
I'll try to get it done.

65
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:06,319
If I fail,

66
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,879
I'll find another way.

67
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:50,160
(I'm Murong Jinghe,
third prince of Daliang.)

68
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,800
(Let me enter the palace now.)

69
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,240
(I must see His Majesty.)

70
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:56,920
Father,

71
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:59,000
I've already secured Zhao's surrender.

72
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:01,079
Here are Zhao's population
and land records.

73
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,560
Please inspect it.

74
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:08,540
(Population and Land Register)

75
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:12,800
Father,

76
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,399
greedy for glory, Xuanlie

77
00:05:14,399 --> 00:05:15,519
forced the attack against Zhao

78
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,000
and hunted me down along the way.

79
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,519
He also seized
Zhao's royal treasures for himself.

80
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,759
That's a grave insult to you.

81
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,160
How dare he!

82
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,480
For some credits,

83
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:26,319
he'd even hunt his own brother

84
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,839
and lie to us all?

85
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:30,240
Why doesn't he just take
this throne instead?

86
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:32,000
Father, it's...

87
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,800
Silence!

88
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,759
Guards, drag her out!

89
00:05:34,959 --> 00:05:36,079
This must be a misunderstanding!

90
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,040
Father, please!

91
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,560
This must be your family's scheming.

92
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,839
Mercy, Father! Mercy!

93
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,639
Hear my decree.

94
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,240
Father!

95
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,639
- Relieve Xuanlie of command.
- Father!

96
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,399
He'll be guarding

97
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,720
the imperial mausoleum!

98
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:52,439
My son,

99
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,199
you've suffered a lot.

100
00:05:55,959 --> 00:05:57,399
The title of Crown Prince

101
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,480
shall be yours.

102
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:09,839
Thank you, Father.

103
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,720
With Prince Xuanlie holding the army,

104
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,519
he'll rebel out of desperation.

105
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:19,879
Don't worry.

106
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,720
I've prepared for this.

107
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:36,759
Jinghe.

108
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,720
Murong Xuanlie has indeed rebelled.

109
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:39,839
This is our chance.

110
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,959
Stick to the plan.

111
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:42,319
We'll split into two groups.

112
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,079
Mei Lin, listen to me.

113
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,399
I've prepared for everything,

114
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:49,600
but if anything...

115
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,079
There is no "if."

116
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:53,279
Deal with Murong Xuanlie.

117
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,720
I'll kill the Emperor.

118
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,839
We'll both make it out alive.

119
00:07:49,820 --> 00:07:51,780
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

